ATTRIBUTION NOTE:

This software implements the methodology described in:

Petsakou A, Sapsis TP, Blau J (2015). "Circadian rhythms in Rho1 activity 
regulate neuronal plasticity and network hierarchy." Cell, 162(4):823-835.
doi: 10.1016/j.cell.2015.07.010

The original MATLAB implementation was developed by:
- Afroditi Petsakou (Department of Biology, New York University)
- Themistoklis P. Sapsis (MIT, Department of Mechanical Engineering)
- Justin Blau (Department of Biology, New York University)

This Python implementation is an independent reimplementation of the published
methodology and is not affiliated with or endorsed by the original authors or
their institutions.
